project:
Welcome to this menu test project. 

Press spacebar to bring up the menu or close it again, pick your option using the arrow keys and press Z to select it. 

When you're on one of the numbered layouts, press backspace to return here. 

Or if you'd prefer to use the gamepad, you can navigate with either the d-pad or left stick. Bring up or close the menu using the Start button, pick an option using A and return to the main layout using B.
